delta change log:
Robots:
	-added setMovesRemaining(): refreshes the robots moves
	-added setCanShoot(): changes the robots canShoot var to true
	-getMovement(): returns the max distance a robot can move (assuming it has all it's moves)
	-initSprites(): loads the corresponding image for each robot
	-getStartingCoord(int direction): gets the coordinate this robot starts at
	-getColour(): gives the colour of the robot
	-getDirection(): gives the direction the robot is facing
	-getRange():gets the range of the robot
	-receiveMsgTest(): a function for testing messaging
	-mailFull(): returns if the inbox is full or not
	-getInbox(): returns the inbox of the robot
	-getSprite(): returns the sprite for the robot
	-getCurrentRotation(): gets the robots current rotation in radians